---
title: Jerk Chicken Burger and Charred Pineapple with Green Onion Aioli and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Mild Caribbean Jerk spice is such a party for your mouth that we had to step up every element of this lively dish. From the delicious caramelized pineapple to the oven-baked sweet potato wedges, each colourful bite is a delight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jerk-chicken-burger-and-charred-pineapple-98d8bbb8.jpg
